Mods.Name: PinkCore
Mods.Author: Pink, StackDoubleFlow, Lillie, RedBrumbler
description: PinkCore is a core mod that ports over many required features which ensure a smooth PC-Like experience. This includes adding information to your game such as Mappers names, Mod Requirements, Custom Colours, Custom Difficulty names, Burn Marks, Chromalite, and more! Please visit our website https://www.questmodding.com for details on what this mod does and why you have this mod. If you require assistance, please head to our discord located in the website.
